! Commands

!! add (producer)

add [queue] [bytes] [data]//

 OK ACCEPTED//
 [id]

 NOK REJECTED//
 [reason]

!! reserve (worker)

reserve [queue]

 OK RESERVED//
 [id] [bytes] [data]

 NOK NO JOBS

!! report (worker)
report [id] [status] [bytes] [data]//

!! status (producer)

status [id]//


 OK <status> <bytes> <data>


! Lifecycle diagram
{{{

 P:add              W:reserve                W:report OK
--------> [QUEUED] ------------> [RESERVED] ---------------> [PROCESSED] 
             ^                     |  |
              \  W:report TMPFAIL  |  |  W:report PERMFAIL 
               --------------------'  '--------------------> [NEEDS ATTENTION]
}}}
                                   
                                      

 


